title: Kenny Davern part 2 Interview by Monk Rowe - 3/16/2001 - Clearwater Beach, FL
description:
In our second interview, Kenny Davern shares poignant memories of the moment that inspired his jazz path, his first road gig, bandstand communication, and opinions about Pee Wee Russell, John Coltrane and Ken Burns' "Jazz."
